            "creation_date": 1329176446,
            "body": "<ol>\n<li>Figure how to do it in JavaScript<\/li>\n<li>Encapsulate that in a JS function.<\/li>\n<li>Call the function from the applet.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n\n<p>That way, at least it is easier to debug the JS and or JS/applet interaction separately.<\/p>\n",
